      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "The relevance of the <code>JAVA_HOME</code> variable is a tenacious myth. Java 1.0 and 1.1 used this variable but since then (for a quarter century now), this variable is not used by Java at all. Only some 3rd party tools use this variable as a convention to find the Java installation."
