    "answer_id" : 27986808,
    "question_id" : 15796855,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case, PATH was properly SET but PATHEXT has been cleared by me by mistake with .exe extension. That why window can't find java or anything .exe application from command prompt. Hope it can help someone. </p>\n"
